        "subject": "LU-2808 lod: create striping on truncate",
        "message": "LU-2808 lod: create striping on truncate\n\nTruncating a stripeless file to a non zero size will now create\nstriping, alleviating the need to truncates from OSP layer.  Delete\ntest sanity 27q (append to truncated file with all OSTs full should\nfail) and rewrite sanity 34a-d (checking if various situations create\nstriping on a file).\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Icc2942c70a4ab82a14688f55ae023411cd15ee8b\n"
      },
